<font size=2><table width="100%" bgcolor="#004b97"><font color=#d2d200><b>Bastion of Thunder Entrance</b></font>&nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=1><a style="color: #ffffff" href="mailto:jcsmith@amazinghideaways.com?subject=Regarding: Bastion of Thunder Entrance">Submit Info</a></font></table>
<font color=white><br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Classes:</b></font> Any<br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Recommended Level</b>:</font> 61<br><b><font color=#d2d200>Quest Rating:</b></font> 
Very Good



<br>
<br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Starting NPC:</b></font> <a style="color:#ffffff" href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Askr%20the%20Lost%22">Askr the Lost</a><br>

<b><font color=#d2d200>Starting Zone:</font></b> Plane of Storms<br>

<b><font color=#d2d200>Related Zones:</font></b> Bastion of Thunder<br>







<br><b>Related NPCs:</b><br><a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Faruek%20the%20Bold%22">Faruek the Bold</a><br>


<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Laruken%20the%20Rigid%22">Laruken the Rigid</a><br>


<a href="http://www.eqspoilers.com/cgi-bin/eqs/webdata_pro.pl?_cgifunction=Search&_layout=eqbestiaryfull&eqbestiary.mob_name=%22Pendubk%20the%20Turbulent%22">Pendubk the Turbulent</a><br>


<br><b>Reward(s)</b>:<br>

<font color=#d2d200>Entrance to the Bastion of Thunder</font><br>

<br>
<font color=#d2d200><b>Description:</b></font><br>
This quest grants entrance in to the Bastion of Thunder. <BR><BR>This spoiler is given in no nonsense format.<BR><BR>1) Obtain a Giant Head from any of the giants types in Plane of Storms.<BR><BR>2) Give the Giant Head to Askr the Lost in the cave in Plane of Storms(near the zone out). After doing so tell him, "it was me". He will give you a container.<BR><BR>3) Obtain the following items from the three different giant types in the Plane of Storms:<BR><BR>Ocean Giants - Beard<BR>Desert Giants - Bone<BR>Forest Giants - Sash<BR><BR>4) Combine those three items in to the Container that Askr the Lost gave you. <BR><BR>5) Give Askr the Lost the combined container. You will receive a character flag at this point.<BR><BR>6) Ask Askr, "what bastion of thunder". He will give you another container back.<BR><BR>7) Obtain two differnet Esoteric Talismans. These are dropped from the named giants in the Plane of Storms. These are often referred to as mini-bosses. There are two of these from each giant type. These are Faruek the Bold, Laruken the Rigid, Pendubk the Turbulent, Solnebk the Unruly, Zertuken the Unyielding and Bittrik the Unkempt. Each giant type drops a different Esoteric. You two different Esoterics. The easiest of the two to get are from Forest and Desert Giants. Ocean giants are a bit more difficult to fight and to pull. <BR><BR>7) Combine the two Esoteric Talisman in to the Container that Askr the Lost gave you.<BR><BR>8) Give the combined container to Askr the Lost and you will receive your Character Flag.<BR><BR>9) Enter the Bastion of Thunder from the Plane of Storms entrance(-105,-430) the first time that you enter. After that point you may enter from the Plane of Tranquility.<br><br>
<br>
<b><font color=#d2d200>Submitted By:</font></b> Midi Brell<br><br>


